thread.title_full: Auto Europe US reviewed by MANFRED BRAIG

author: MANFRED BRAIG
title: MANFRED BRAIG
text: I have been doing business with Kemwel // Auto Europe US for many years...they are top notch, always great service, good rates and they are reliable and dependable. Lucy, my agent today was very efficient, she understood what I needed and made the proper suggestions. I booked again 2 different car rentals today for my forthcoming trip to Germany, I am a happy camper, thank you, AutoEurope US, Manfred H. Braig
